{"word":"G3971 - πατρῷος - patrōios - pat-ro'-os - Of fathers","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">πατρῷος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">patrōios</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">pat-ro'-os</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Of fathers</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"முன்னோர்களுடைய - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"descending from father to son or from ancestors to their posterity as it were by right of inheritance; received from the fathers"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G3962 - πατήρ - patḗr - pat-ayr'/3962\">G3962</a>; <i>paternal</i>, that is, <i>hereditary:</i> - of fathers.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G3962/3962\">G3962</a>, <a href=\"#/G3965/3965\">G3965</a>, <a href=\"#/G3966/3966\">G3966</a>, <a href=\"#/G3967/3967\">G3967</a>, <a href=\"#/G3968/3968\">G3968</a>, <a href=\"#/G3971/3971\">G3971</a>, <a href=\"#/G540/540\">G540</a>"}]}